ent-RMCBeltHolsterNailgun = Кастомизированный пояс для гвоздодёра
    .desc = Выродок инженерной мысли какого-то пустынного рейнджера, созданный чтобы носить компактный гвоздодёр и магазины к нему.
ent-RMCM300SOCOMBelt = Пояс для боеприпасов .458 SOCOM M300
    .desc = Пояс, предназначенный для хранения крупнокалиберных патронов .458 SOCOM для тяжёлой винтовки XM88.
ent-RMCM82FHolster = Пояс M276 с кобурой для сигнального пистолета M82F
    .desc = M276 является стандартным снаряжением ККМП. Он состоит из модульного ремня с различными фиксаторами. Эта версия предназначена для сигнального пистолета M82F и 18-ти запасных ракет.
ent-RMCM82FHolsterFilled = { ent-RMCM82FHolster }
    .suffix = Filled
    .desc = { ent-RMCM82FHolster.desc }
ent-RMCBeltSPPBrown = Пояс 6B80
    .desc = 6B80 - это устаревший, но не менее пригодный пояс для аммуниции, раньше стоявший на вооружении СССП. До сих пор используется охраной и отдельными солдатами за свой дизайн.
ent-RMCBeltMachineGunner = M804 heavygunner storage rig
    .desc = The M804 heavygunner storage rig is an M276 pattern toolbelt rig modified to carry ammunition for heavy machinegun systems, and engineering tools for the gunner.
ent-RMCMedicalL75RCM = L75 pattern medical storage rig
    .desc = The L75 is the standard load-bearing equipment of the RCM. It consists of a modular belt with various clips. This version is designed to transport medical supplies and pistol ammunition.
    .suffix = RCM, Medical
ent-RMCMedicalL75RCMFillPara = { ent-RMCMedicalL75RCM }
    .suffix = Paramarine, Survivor, Filled, Medical
    .desc = { ent-RMCMedicalL75RCM.desc }
ent-RMCBeltRCM = L70 pattern ammo load rig
    .desc = Good for carrying around extra ammo in the heat of the jungle. Made of special rot-resistant fabric.
    .suffix = RCM, Ammo
ent-RMCBeltUtilityGeneralRCM = L26 general utility belt
    .desc = A small, lightweight pouch that can be clipped onto armor to provide additional storage. This new RCM model, while uncomfortable, can also be clipped around the waist.
    .suffix = PVP, RCM
ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolRCM = L80 general pistol holster rig
    .desc = The L80 is the standard load-bearing equipment of the Royal Crown Marines. It consists of a modular belt with various clips. This version has a holster assembly that allows one to carry the most common pistols. It also contains side pouches that can store most pistol magazines.
    .suffix = RCM, Pistol Belt
ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolPara = paramarine load bearing rig
    .desc = A sturdy belt fitted with a black leather holster designed for RCM Paramarines. A large utility pouch and several smaller compartments provide ample space for extra ammunition and field essentials — standard gear for Paramarines dropping into hostile territory.
    .suffix = Paramarine, Survivor
ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolParaM44 = { ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolPara }
    .suffix = Paramarine, Survivor, Filled, Warwick
    .desc = { ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolPara.desc }
ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolParaM44Random = { ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolPara }
    .suffix = Paramarine, Survivor, Random, Warwick
    .desc = { ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolPara.desc }
ent-RMCBeltHolsterPistolParaCustom = paramarine custom load-bearing rig
    .desc = A modified RCM Paramarine belt featuring a black leather holster with gold inlay, a large utility pouch, and several smaller compartments provide ample space for extra ammunition and field essentials — standard gear for Paramarines dropping into hostile territory.
    .suffix = Paramarine, Survivor, Filled, L54 Custom
ent-RMCBeltRoyalMortar = L79 pattern load-bearing rig
    .desc = An L79 pattern load-bearing rig configured to carry support ammunition for either the light mortar or L989A2 multiple grenade launcher, along with a sidearm & magazine. Made of special rot-resistant fabric.
    .suffix = PVE, RCM, Filled
ent-RMCBeltRoyalMortarFilled = { ent-RMCBeltRoyalMortar }
